snippet.title: Boti: Byteland Overclocked | Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the prologue FOR FREE! 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2426410

Wishlist the full game! 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2161050

Boti: Byteland Overclocked is a 3D platformer inspired by the classics. All your favorite platforming moves are here! Use and chain them to discover fantastic combos. Double jump, dash, hover, and glide to explore a vibrant and colorful world!

A great adventure awaits you! Follow us to be ready when the game releases on September 15!
